OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bill help for firms 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fexpected to be halved      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Business groups are expecting          
OL,6, government help with their energy bills
OL,7, to be halved after March, when the     
OL,8, existing package of support expires.   
OL,10,FAllies of the chancellor said the      
OL,11,Fsupport would be significantly lower to
OL,12,Fprotect the public finances from       
OL,13,Fvolatile energy markets.               
OL,15,FGas and electricity prices have been   
OL,16,Ffixed for firms until the end of March,
OL,17,Fbut many want the support to continue. 
OL,19,FThe revised scheme is expected to run  
OL,20,Ffor 12 months until March 2024.        
